column12: Yes, Yonah. It's yours, and yours alone.
You look...bigger than before. Like you've grown up.
Well yeah, I guess you haven't seen me for a while.
Have I been asleep this whole time?
It's almost like I'm a princess from some fairy tale.
Oh, Yonah. I'm so happy to have you back.
You and your sister, you have a good life, okay?
You could stay with us, you know.
You know how it is. I got my own shit to take care of.
Personal shit, all right? Anyway...take it easy, yeah?
For the longest time, I heard someone telling me how they wanted to see the light...
And now, they can finally see it.
